zboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#333333>(5/11/02 5:35:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Suit of Sentient Armor Question</span><hr size=1> I was just wondering if anyone who is level 55 (my mage is half a blue from 55, just farming AAXP at dark elves in neriak, heheh) has been successful at solo pulling the suits.  I'm currently twinking a SK and I want a full suit of sentient.  Any information about the &quot;suits of sentient armor&quot; in wakening land, would be a great help to me.  Thank You!! <p>Anitalynn WindRyder<br>
54th Level Elementalist<br>
<br>
Rtwo Dtwo<br>
32nd Level Necromancer<br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uxanicrimsonheart.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xani Crimsonheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#333333>(5/13/02 12:12:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Suit of Sentient Armor Question</span><hr size=1> They can be killed by a solo Mage.  However, they're clumped so tight though, it's not possible to single pull them unless you get someone to Harmony. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
