Tailoring - 159<BR>
Baking - 152</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ureeje.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reeje</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#333333>(5/13/02 2:35:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Suit of Sentient Armor Question</span><hr size=1> Just grabb a partner.<br>
<br>
My friend (mage level 55) and me (mage level 54) are farming now the suit in WL. Yes, all the time, the pull will result of 2 suits coming, no matter the pulling spell, no matter the position before pulling. But 2 mages &lt; 56 do a good work here, and exp are not bad. I could see my exp bar move after each pull at 54 level.<br>
<br>
Just be carefull !!!! we were killed in 2 seconds from a corrupted faun. Doesn't have the time to see him, he quad for 240 and backstab for 240. <br>
<br>
 <p>Reeje Beckmul - Mage Erudit <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uelkanah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elkanah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#333333>(5/23/02 8:24:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Suit of Sentient Armor Question</span><hr size=1> There are 2 camps of sents in WL. The one closer to Kael has 4 sents, 2 in front and 2 in back. The other camp has 6 sents also in pairs. Like the above posters have said, it is impossible to single pull the sents without harmony or FD pulling.<br>
<br>
I wouldn't worry about the corrupted faun so long as you pull the sent to the wall. No roamers whatsoever there.<br>
<br>
Sents are easy with a partner.<br>
Solo, I had to chain earth pet 3 times to finish off one sent. Sents have a ton of hp.<br>
<br>
-Elk<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujochangaladar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jochan Galadar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 292<br> <font color=#333333>(5/30/02 10:25:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Suit of Sentient Armor Question</span><hr size=1> For a magician, you will find that you cannot single pull them until 57.  Then it's trivial. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uqenadayne1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qenadayne1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(6/8/02 1:17:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Suit of Sentient Armor Question</span><hr size=1> The pulling of these is nasty.  I have single pulled them from the house near Kael with the 4 in it.  I was 55th at the time and grouped with 2 friends (druid 54 and Pally 54).  I did not really keep track of how many single pulls I did get, I was using the Malo line of spells.  I did not get many pulls solo, but you can do it, I found standing as far as I could and way to a side, basically the furthest from the one target and at a angle so I was as far from the others at the same time.  This did not always work, so DO NOT plan on it.  Not sure why sometimes it would and others it would not.<br>
<br>
I am just throwing this out there, so if you go and try and you get one or two pulls single you will know that it does not always work.<br>
<br>
Hope this information helps.<br>
<br>
Qenadayne Corpsealot<br>
&quot;Young Pup&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uchaoslordkhorne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ChaosLordKhorne</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 82<br> <font color=#333333>(6/11/02 1:06:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Suit of Sentient Armor Question</span><hr size=1> You can reliably single pull them at 56. I spent a little while there at 56 and over a few hundred pulls never got more than one. <p>Awer - Level 57 High Elf Magician<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=164959">Hearteater</a> - Level 53 Iskar Monk<BR>Proud Guildleader of Dawn Breaker - Prexus<BR>ChaosLordKhorne<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usanduin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sanduin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(6/13/02 8:40:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   safe spot too</span><hr size=1> also, you can sit right down at the camp with the 6 suits (there's some room, uhm, east from it i think), and unless trained, you'll never ever get roamers there. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uaj0302.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AJ0302</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span>